==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: jīnzhāo yŏu jiŭ jīnzhāo zuì
===Etymology===
Literally: Today we have wine, so today we get drunk.
===Idiom===
'''[[今朝]][[有]][[酒]][[今朝]][[醉]]'''
# describes someone with attitude of instant gratification; describes someone who never thinks about the future; here today, gone tomorow.
#: ''[[今天]][[的]][[年輕人]][[也]][[應該]][[為]][[他們]][[的]][[後人]][[艱苦]][[奮鬥]]，[[不能]][[抱]][[著]]“'''今朝有酒今朝醉'''”[[的]][[態度]][[過]][[日子]]。'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[今天]][[的]][[年轻人]][[也]][[应该]][[为]][[他们]][[的]][[后人]][[艰苦]][[奋斗]]，[[不能]][[抱]][[着]]“'''今朝有酒今朝醉'''”[[的]][[态度]][[过]][[日子]]。'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''Today's youth must struggle diligently for the sake of those who will come after them.  They must not while away their time with an attitude of '''here today, gone tomorow'''.''
